Cyberpunk style: A towering corporate skyscraper at night, its floors stacked vertically with glowing windows. At the bottom floors, the windows emit harsh red and orange warning lights, screens showing chaotic data streams and declining graphs. As the eye travels upward, each successive floor gradually shifts in color—amber, then yellow, then increasingly bright green and teal. At the penthouse level, the windows radiate an impossibly serene, almost heavenly cyan glow with calm, simple displays. The building acts as a visual filter, transforming reality as information ascends. Neon rain streaks down the dark purple sky, and holographic birds circle the optimistic apex. The architecture features brutalist concrete mixed with circuit-board patterns and exposed fiber optic cables running between floors like glowing arteries, suggesting the flow of increasingly distorted information traveling upward through the corporate machine.
